{
  "texts": [
    "LLM can analyze a large amount of existing circuit design documents to extract key information such as functional modules and interface specifications to define the design space for EA.",
    "EA can optimize circuit topology, component selection and layout to meet multi-objective optimization of performance, power consumption and cost.",
    "LLM can also generate initial circuit design schemes for EA with reference to existing design cases.",
    "EA further optimizes the circuit topology through LLM-guided variation and selection.",
    "Among them, the design schemes and reports generated by LLM can be used as training data to improve LLM's ability in this field."
  ]
}